name: Head, 2016
description:
oil on canvas, paste up, markers, acrylic, photoshop, cm 100x150
I'm really bound with this painting on canvas; I used to paste up this subject among others in the streets some year ago and it was a sort of iconic image of my work. For this painting I decided to paste the cutout directly on an abstract canvas on which I was working on and paint again on it. The result is a sort of compendium of my practice as a painter with some little but intense link with street art.4000x2700px png
